  <main>
    <section id="blockchain-section">
      <h2>Blockchain</h2>
      <p>Blockchain is a decentralized, distributed ledger technology that records transactions across multiple computers in a way that ensures the security, transparency, and immutability of the data.</p>
      <p>It's the technology behind cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum.</p>
    </section>
    <section id="web3-section">
      <h2>Web3</h2>
      <p>Web3 refers to the next generation of the internet, where decentralized applications (dApps) built on blockchain technology enable peer-to-peer interactions without the need for intermediaries.</p>
      <p>It enables users to interact directly with blockchain networks, access decentralized finance (DeFi) platforms, and more.</p>
    </section>
